Online Management Training Programme

# A charter for students to help them level up in their career

# build a successful career and gain experience

SIMTRAKs Online Management Training Programme is an initiative to provide training to students who aspire a career in the corporate sector, to gain practical knowledge and experience in managing live projects and tasks.
This program focuses on creating an industry ready management trainee in different domains through flexible, focused, live training sessions which will help to develop skills like :-

  • Communication Skills
  • Confidence
  • Presentation Skills
  • Leadership Skills
  • Management Training
  • Networking
    And many more
